## `test_interop_ripgrep_finds_content(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-interop-5 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: external tool behavior -->

### Postconditions

```python
if not HAS_RG:
    pytest.skip("ripgrep not installed")

(mount / "a.md").write_text("hello needle world")
(mount / "b.md").write_text("no match here")

out = subprocess.run(
    ["rg", "needle", str(mount)],
    check=True, capture_output=True, text=True,
)
assert "a.md" in out.stdout
assert "b.md" not in out.stdout
```

