## `test_interop_cp_recursive(mount, tmp_path)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-interop-7 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: external tool behavior -->

### Postconditions

```python
src = tmp_path / "src"
src.mkdir()
(src / "a.txt").write_text("x")
(src / "dir").mkdir()
(src / "dir" / "b.txt").write_text("y")

subprocess.run(["cp", "-r", str(src), str(mount / "dst")], check=True)

assert (mount / "dst" / "a.txt").read_text() == "x"
assert (mount / "dst" / "dir" / "b.txt").read_text() == "y"
```

