## `test_interop_find_traverses(mount)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-interop-8 -->
<!-- trace: skipped -->
<!-- trace_skip_reason: external tool behavior -->

### Postconditions

```python
(mount / "a").mkdir()
(mount / "a" / "f").write_text("x")
(mount / "a" / "sub").mkdir()
(mount / "a" / "sub" / "g").write_text("y")

out = subprocess.run(
    ["find", str(mount / "a"), "-type", "f"],
    check=True, capture_output=True, text=True,
)
lines = out.stdout.strip().split("\n")
assert sorted(lines) == sorted([str(mount / "a" / "f"), str(mount / "a" / "sub" / "g")])
```

